  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male or female, at least 18 years of age.

          -  Documented compensated HBeAg negative CHB defined by baseline HBV serology, DNA and
             ALT criteria.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Co-infection with HCV, HDV, or HIV.

          -  Prior therapy with nucleos(t)ides in NAÏVE patient and prior treatment with lamivudine
             in patients with suboptimal response to adefovir.

          -  History of hepatic decompensation

          -  History of malignancy

          -  Patient has one or more additional known primary or secondary causes of liver disease
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
